headline: JPMorgan Raises VeriSign (VRSN) Target as Domain Trends Improve
summary: VeriSign, Inc. (NASDAQ:VRSN) is included among the 13 Companies that Just Started Paying Dividends. On January 6, JPMorgan analyst Alexei Gogolev raised his price objective on VeriSign, Inc. (NASDAQ:VRSN) to $271 from $270. The analyst kept a Neutral rating on the stock. In a research note, he pointed to steady improvement in the .com domain […]
